import React, { useState } from "react";
import {
  Col,
  Button,
  Form,
  FormGroup,
  Label,
  Input,
  FormText,
} from "reactstrap";

export const SignIn = () => {
  
  return (
    <Form>
      <FormGroup row>
        <Label for="exampleEmail" sm={2}>
          Email
        </Label>
        <Col sm={10}>
          <Input
            type="email"
            name="email"
            id="exampleEmail"
            placeholder="with a placeholder"
          />
        </Col>
      </FormGroup>
      <FormGroup row>
        <Label for="examplePassword" sm={2}>
          Password
        </Label>
        <Col sm={10}>
          <Input
            type="password"
            name="password"
            id="examplePassword"
            placeholder="password placeholder"
          />
        </Col>
      </FormGroup>

      <FormGroup check row>
        <Col sm={{ size: 10, offset: 2 }}>
          <Button>Submit</Button>
        </Col>
      </FormGroup>
    </Form>
  );
};
